cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with tracking multiple vehicles using multiple sensors, which is a common problem in robotics (cs.RO). The use of high-resolution sensors suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) techniques may be employed. The proposed filter is a probabilistic model, which is a common approach in control systems (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Gaussian processes and fusion mapping suggests that machine learning (cs.LG) techniques may also be employed.
